          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "intro_title",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Your Trusted Phoenix Plumbing Experts",
                "title_color": "#0f172a",
                "typography_typography": "custom",
                "typography_font_family": "Space Grotesk",
                "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 40},
                "typography_font_weight": "700",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "intro_text1",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>When plumbing issues arise in your Phoenix home, you need a team you can trust. At Desert Flow Plumbing, we've been serving the Valley for over 15 years with exceptional service, fair pricing, and lasting solutions. From minor leaks to major emergencies, our certified plumbers have the expertise to handle any job with precision and care.</p>",
                "text_color": "#64748b",
                "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 18},
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "intro_text2",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>We understand that plumbing problems don't wait for convenient times. That's why we offer same-day service and 24/7 emergency availability. Our commitment to customer satisfaction has made us one of the most recommended plumbing companies in Phoenix.</p>",
                "text_color": "#64748b",
                "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 18},
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
